name: Sando Aqua Monster
Lore: 'Huge creature that is feline in nature and moves on its hind legs. Slow movement makes it difficult for the monster to feed but whenever a confrontation arises it always wins.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Cancels Colo Claw Fish. While no card here, you may draw destiny and place it face-up here. If you are about to draw a card for weapon or battle destiny, you may instead use card here, then place it in Lost Pile. (Immune to Alter.)',
